elog_lib CHANGELOG
==================

- v1.1.0 | Mar 06 2026:
  [New] CEF output module with ArcSight Common Event Format (v0) support
  [New] CEF severity mapping (debug=1, info=3, warn=5, error=7, critical=10)
  [New] CEF header and extension escaping (pipe, backslash, equals, newline)
  [New] Syslog UDP output module with RFC 5424 and RFC 3164 format support
  [New] Fire-and-forget UDP delivery via /dev/udp with nc fallback
  [New] Syslog severity mapping and PRI calculation (facility * 8 + severity)
  [New] Configurable syslog payload format (classic, json, cef)
  [New] Event context staging for SIEM handler access to structured event data
  [New] 26 new tests across 07-elog-cef.bats and 08-elog-syslog-udp.bats

- v1.0.0 | Mar 06 2026:
  [New] Standalone elog_lib repository extracted from BFD elog_lib.sh v1.0.0
  [New] Deterministic log file architecture: dual log model (application + audit)
  [New] elog_init() for log environment setup (directory, permissions, symlinks)
  [New] elog_logrotate_snippet() generator for logrotate config
  [New] Output module registry with parallel indexed arrays (file, audit_file, syslog_file, stdout)
  [New] Source filtering per output module (all, elog, event)
  [New] Log truncation support via ELOG_LOG_MAX_LINES (inode-safe)
  [New] Legacy symlink support via ELOG_LEGACY_LOG
  [New] Backward-compatible elog() API with dispatch-based routing
  [New] BATS test suite with batsman CI (9-OS matrix)
  [New] elog_event() structured event envelope with JSON dispatch to audit log
  [New] Event taxonomy with 23 canonical types across 7 categories
  [New] Default severity mapping via _elog_event_severity() (error/warn/info)
  [New] elog_critical() convenience wrapper completing 5-level API symmetry
  [New] Backward compatibility test suite validating no-init drop-in pattern
  [New] README.md with full API reference, event taxonomy, and usage guide
  [Change] Extract _elog_auto_enable() helper from elog() for DRY pre-init fallback
